**Learning outcomes**

**Skills** 
• Convert numbers between various representations. 
• Implement arithmetic operations. 

**Knowledge** 
• Concepts of base and radix. Conversion between bases, including octal, hexadecimal and 
binary. 
• Floating point numbers: concepts of mantissa, exponent, significand; concept of 
normalisation and steps involved. 
• IEEE 754: format, single precision and double precision; number ranges; algorithm for 
converting from other format; codes for zero; addition/subtraction; underflow/overflow 
conditions
